description: Mercure integration — real-time event streaming.
files[1]{file,type,summary}:
  RunEventPublisher.php,readonly final class,"This class publishes run events to a Mercure hub, enabling real-time updates for clients subscribed to specific run topics. It abstracts the communication with the Mercure infrastructure to decouple event publishing from the core business logic."